messages.text: u didn’t see it on the news?
no, thats the question. wat did happen.
we all r. an hour ago millions of people just disappeared…
one min they were there, next they were gone
One woman was at home cooking with her husband, and the next she vanished into thin air. Her husband saw it.
Kids vanishing. Moms, dad, sisters, brothers.
that’s y i txted, make sure ur ok
Dad txted back, hadn’t heard from my mom. He hasn’t either.
At work. She could just be busy. I hope she hasn’t vanished.
Screw him. I don’t care. I hope he’s vanished.
Nah. It’s recent though. We broke up a week ago.
I’m actually really worried about my mom though.
What if she got into one of the crashes.
im sure shes fine. Kims always been a trooper. call her office and see if anyone has seen her.
Good idea. Any of your family gone.
we’re all here which is strange
No! That’s great! How is that strange?
everyone had at least 1 person taken, not us
or designed, im not sure bout all this
dont get me wrong. love that i still have my family.
Does anyone have an idea as to who or what this is?
some theories, aliens, rapture, warfare, but no one knows for sure
have u checked on ur mom?
Just about to call. Hold on.
She’s vanished. She was one of them.
o my god… im so sorry:(
can u think of any reason y she might b taken?
No :( Not that comes to mind,
Ya, said he’s just checking in. See if I’m ok.
I know. Shame. I’d trade him for my mom any day.
dang, mustve ended really bad between u 2 then…
wat did happen? if u dont mind me askin
yep. think everyone did. check the news
My TV is still rebooting, what’s happening?
Yep. So you heard that thing too??
sure did. news says they did 2, cut out their power 4 a few minutes, apparently it was a global thing
A very, very, very loud one.
do you believe in the rapture
would kinda make sense. my family’s not believers i guess
but wat if. wasnt ur mom pretty devout??
Stop. I will not let you pawn my mom’s disappearance on a figment of someone’s imagination.
thought vanishing into thin air was fiction, now look at this
A METEOR JUST FELL FROM THE SKY
OMG, one just smashed the house next 2 me
If it lands on my house, ill be gone anyway!
